项目，体积庞大，没人能全懂。公司要求每次修改都要注释作者 /时间 /修改内容，由于人员水平参差不齐，导致注释完备但代码难懂。部分文件几经变迁，混杂着各种业务代码与黑魔法，例如几十行的逻辑判断，旁边有各年代留下的为什么加这个判断的注释。\n请问有什么方案可以管理代码的变更，优雅的反应代码如何到今天这样子，而只需对代码做最少的更改？</p>\n","last_modified":1611541869,"replies":11,"id":748056},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1610122510","name":"programmer","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1610122510","title":"程序员","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","topics":42886,"footer":"","header":"While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.","title_alternative":"Programmer","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1610122510","stars":7213,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":300,"parent_node_name":"computer"},"member":{"username":"cweijan","website":"","github":"cweijan","psn":"","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/12d5/1f5d/267965_mini.png?m=1611540448","bio":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/cweijan","tagline":"","twitter":"","created":1511016048,"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/12d5/1f5d/267965_mini.png?m=1611540448","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/12d5/1f5d/267965_mini.png?m=1611540448","location":"","btc":"","id":267965},"last_reply_by":"cweijan","last_touched":1611543761,"title":"解放生产力! 全新开源数据库客户端!","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/748041","created":1611540632,"content":"使用条件: vscode 为你的主力工具.(该客户端为 vscode 扩展)\r\n\r\n文档地址: https://github.com/cweijan/vscode-database-client/blob/master/README_CN.md\r\n\r\n作为一个后端, 每天除了写代码就是看数据库, 然而市面上主流的数据库客户端用起来总不是很顺手, 故开发了这个客户端, 经过一年迭代, 现在日常常用功能体验已经超越 Datagrip 、Navicat 等主流客户端.\r\n\r\n相比上次在 v2 发布, 本次的更新了以下功能:\r\n\r\n1. 之前只支持 mysql, 现在额外增加了 PostgreSql 、SqlServer 、Redis 和 ES 的支持!\r\n![]( https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/007HN2KHgy1gmzptzpkwej30yw0exdke.jpg)\r\n2. 表格视图重构, 如今视觉效果打满, 同时颜色跟随 vscode 主题.\r\n![]( https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/007HN2KHgy1gmzptzhff7j30rz0engnd.jpg)\r\n3. sql 提示优化, 感受丝滑般的 sql 编写体验\r\n![]( https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/007HN2KHgy1gmzptzale4j30j406j0su.jpg)\r\n4. 额外增加了一个视图容器, 用于显示 redis 和 ElasticSearch\r\n5. 视图菜单增加了中文 i18n, 不用担心看不懂英文了!","content_rendered":"<p>使用条件: vscode 为你的主力工具.(该客户端为 vscode 扩展)</p>\n<p>文档地址: <a href=\"https://github.com/cweijan/vscode-database-client/blob/master/README_CN.md\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://github.com/cweijan/vscode-database-client/blob/master/README_CN.md</a></p>\n<p>作为一个后端, 每天除了写代码就是看数据库, 然而市面上主流的数据库客户端用起来总不是很顺手, 故开发了这个客户端, 经过一年迭代, 现在日常常用功能体验已经超越 Datagrip 、Navicat 等主流客户端.</p>\n<p>相比上次在 v2 发布, 本次的更新了以下功能:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>之前只支持 mysql, 现在额外增加了 PostgreSql 、SqlServer 、Redis 和 ES 的支持!\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/007HN2KHgy1gmzptzpkwej30yw0exdke.jpg\"/></li>\n<li>表格视图重构, 如今视觉效果打满, 同时颜色跟随 vscode 主题.\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/007HN2KHgy1gmzptzhff7j30rz0engnd.jpg\"/></li>\n<li>sql 提示优化, 感受丝滑般的 sql 编写体验\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/007HN2KHgy1gmzptzale4j30j406j0su.jpg\"/></li>\n<li>额外增加了一个视图容器, 用于显示 redis 和 ElasticSearch</li>\n<li>视图菜单增加了中文 i18n, 不用担心看不懂英文了!</li>\n</ol>\n","last_modified":1611540632,"replies":11,"id":748041},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1594743680","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1594743680","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":167684,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1594743680","stars":3149,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":12,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"username":"VVVV7","website":"","github":null,"psn":null,"avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/8d466cc74fe2b112009d8